,{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"그거 정~말로 공감돼요!\n어쩐지 그곳에 있는 사람들을 보면\n어떤 학교인지 알 것 같은 느낌이 들죠.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"event201-04-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"나도 스케줄 때문에 몇 군데 학교 축제에 불려 간 적은 있는데,\n대학에 따라서 정말 분위기가 달라.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event201-04-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"점점 수험도 다가왔고,\n진로를 정하기 전에 실제로 자신의 피부로\n학교 분위기를 느껴 두고 싶으니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event201-04-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"과연~ 수험이라~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"serious02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event201-04-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"tal